# ——— Canonical domain + HTTPS ———
https://www.perfectlivesound.com/*   https://perfectlivesound.com/:splat   301!
http://perfectlivesound.com/*        https://perfectlivesound.com/:splat   301!
http://www.perfectlivesound.com/*    https://perfectlivesound.com/:splat   301!

# ——— Rute vechi (.html) -> rute "frumoase" ———
/galerie.html    /galerie/    301!
/servicii.html   /servicii/   301!
/contact.html    /contact/    301!

# (opțional) Trailing slash pentru cele 3 secțiuni dacă se accesează fără /
/galerie        /galerie/     301!
/servicii       /servicii/    301!
/contact        /contact/     301!

# ——— 404 fallback ———
/*   /404.html   404
